# =============================================
#  .gitignore — Personal Workout
#  Tutto ciò che NON deve finire su GitHub
# =============================================

# --- OS junk ---
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*~

# --- Editor / IDE ---
.idea/
.vscode/
.history/
node_modules/

# --- Backup locali (sicurezza, non versionare) ---
index.original.html
*.bak
*.orig

# --- Deliverable di proposta / preview / esplorazioni di design ---
PROPOSTA_PREVIEW.html
PROPOSTA_PREVIEW copia.html
PROPOSTA_REWORK_PREMIUM_iOS.md
*.copia.*
*\ copia.*
*\ copy.*

# --- File di lavoro / sciolti ---
planksuginocchia
free-exercise-db-main/
free-exercise-db-main.zip

# --- Video sorgente raw (l'app usa solo i *-ios.mp4 ottimizzati) ---
*.webm
**/*.webm
assets/*.mp4
assets/Fix*
assets/Affondi*
assets/Lateral*

# --- Asset non referenziati dall'app ---
assets/exercises/sumo-squat.mp4
assets/exercises/sumo-squat.webm
assets/exercises/toetaps.mov
assets/exercises/toetaps-poster.jpg
assets/exercises/toe-taps.png
assets/exercises/dead-bug.jpg
assets/exercises/glute-bridge.png
assets/exercises/incline-plank-bench.jpg
assets/exercises/incline-push-up.jpg
assets/exercises/plank-shoulder-taps.jpg
assets/exercises/side-leg-raise.jpg
assets/exercises/side-plank-knees.jpg
assets/exercises/squat-hold.jpg

# Nota: `assets/exercises/side-plank.jpg` è MANTENUTO perché usato dall'app
# come fallback statico per "Side plank corto" (advanced/core).
# `assets/exercises/CREDITS.md` è MANTENUTO per attribuzione dei video.
